column10: On Saturday, 12/18, around 5pm, a driver hit a cyclist in the crosswalk. The driver was heading north on Van Dorn and turning right onto Taney. The cyclist was heading south and biking in the crosswalk.  Info was shared. Authorities were not contacted.
